query:
INSERT INTO
            users
            (username, password, email)
        SELECT
            $1, crypt($2, gen_salt('bf')), crypt($3, gen_salt('bf'))
        WHERE NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 
                1 
            FROM 
                users 
            WHERE 
                email = crypt($3, email)
            )
        RETURNING
            id, username, password, email, created_at, last_connection
